        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Control+n          | Move cursor to next physical line.             |
        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Control+left,      | Move cursor to previous word boundary.         |
        | Alt+b              |                                                |
        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
