        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Control+Shift+End  | Select text to end of file.                    |
        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Control+Space,     | Set mark to select text region.                |
        | Control+@          |                                                |
        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
