        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Alt+a              | Select all text.                               |
        +--------------------+------------------------------------------------+
        | Alt+c              | Select current word at first press. Subsequent |
        |                    | press selects entire current line, and the     |
        |                    | third press selects entire text                |
